pageContext.claim: “All of this impeachment nonsense, which is going nowhere, is driving the Stock Market, and your 401K’s, down. But that is exactly what the Democrats want to do. They are willing to hurt the Country, with only the 2020 Election in mind!”
pageContext.analysis: Stocks were falling because of warning signs in the economy, such a recession in the manufacturing sector, not because of the impeachment inquiry.
